description: Creates an empty ipynb file in the specified Apache Spark enabled workgroup. Throws an error if a file in the workgroup with the same name already exists.

parameters.name: WorkGroup
parameters.description: The name of the Spark enabled workgroup in which the notebook will be created.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the ipynb file to be created in the Spark workgroup, without the .ipynb extension.

parameters.name: ClientRequestToken
parameters.description: A unique case-sensitive string used to ensure the request to create the notebook is idempotent (executes only once).

nested_items.name: NotebookId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the notebook.
